===Adjacent townships===
* [[Paw Paw Township, Wabash County, Indiana|Paw Paw Township]] (north)
* [[Lagro Township, Wabash County, Indiana|Lagro Township]] (east)
* [[Liberty Township, Wabash County, Indiana|Liberty Township]] (southeast)
* [[Waltz Township, Wabash County, Indiana|Waltz Township]] (south)
* [[Butler Township, Miami County, Indiana|Butler Township, Miami County]] (southwest)
* [[Erie Township, Miami County, Indiana|Erie Township, Miami County]] (west)
* [[Richland Township, Miami County, Indiana|Richland Township, Miami County]] (northwest)

===Cemeteries===
The township contains these eight cemeteries: Friends, Hebrew, Huff, Martin Luther, Matlock, Memorial Lawns, Richvalley and Wallace.

